Barbara Lang (film actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Lang_(film_actress) 0 Barbara Lang (March 2, 1928 – July 22, 1982) was an American actress and singer. During the 1950s she was one of the many B-level blondes to be promoted as a Marilyn Monroe-type. Barbara_Lang ( March_2_,_1928 – July_22_,_1982 ) was an_American_actress_and_singer .
